title: Reports of attempted stabbing in Jerusalem
text:
Tel Aviv - A Palestinian has been shot in Jerusalem after he allegedly tried to stab Israeli police officers, police say.
Spokesperson Luba Samri was is unable to confirm whether the alleged stabber is dead or injured.
The incident occured at the Damascus Gate into the walled Old City.
